snippet.title: PRICELESS REACTIONS of BABIES; MIRRORS - The FUNNIEST BABY VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Funniest babies and toddlers reactions when they "meet" mirrors for the first time! Their responses are different, some try to talk, others try to escape, some of them just.. fail :D This funny/cute combination will make your day better! So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
